Transmutation
Levels: Bard 1
Components: V, S
Range: Personal
Target: Self.
Duration: 1 round/level

You gain access to a floating "pool" of luck, which manifests as a +2 bonus on attack rolls for the spell's duration. If the extend spell metamagic is used with this spell, the bonus drops to +1.

<i>With an elaborate flourish and call for luck, you toss the dice in your hand into the air. Immediately you feel as though fate favors you, filling you with confidence.</i>